dct_title_s: Rutgers University, New Jersey, Camden campus 1955
dct_description_sm: Map of Camden Campus Area, Rutgers, the State University, South Jersey Division, Camden New Jersey create Oct. 5, 1955 and revised April 2, 1957. College buildings depicted and shaded along with a dashed outline of a Presbyterian church.
